data.description: Come see this cozy 3 bed/ 2bath set on 2.4 acres with a unique floor plan, a spacious fenced backyard and large shop with a large sliding door on the front! Don't forget the concrete patio with the inground pool and the attached 2 car carport and the 2 car garage as well! This home is right off Hwy 57 with easy access to Hwy 441 as well! Call today!
